1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:04,500
Planning a family trip means thirty hours
lost across review sites, maps, and forums —

2
00:00:04,500 --> 00:00:07,500
and you still aren't sure.

3
00:00:07,500 --> 00:00:11,500
HotelZippo replaces all of it
with one conversation.

4
00:00:11,500 --> 00:00:14,500
You just talk. Tell it
who's travelling and where —

5
00:00:14,500 --> 00:00:19,500
a vegetarian family heading to Phuket
with two kids and grandparents —

6
00:00:19,500 --> 00:00:24,500
and it asks the right questions, building a
complete picture of what your family needs.

7
00:00:24,500 --> 00:00:30,000
Then it delivers one confident pick —
backed by family reviews synthesised by AI,

8
00:00:30,000 --> 00:00:33,000
not a wall of links.

9
00:00:33,000 --> 00:00:36,500
And it never buries a dealbreaker.

10
00:00:36,500 --> 00:00:42,000
When a hotel has a real problem, the warning
is right there, above everything else.

11
00:00:42,000 --> 00:00:45,000
Honesty over polish.

12
00:00:45,000 --> 00:00:49,000
Save it, and book it — straight through.

13
00:00:49,000 --> 00:00:53,500
From a single question to a booking
you can trust, in under a minute.

14
00:00:53,500 --> 00:00:56,500
HotelZippo. The family travel concierge.
